These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, epic
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, lemon
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
2. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | musical |
| Food       | kiwi | lemon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, chess
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Hobby   | skydiving | chess |
| Sport      | surfing     | golf  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
