City: edinburgh, colone
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | western  |
| City   | edinburgh | colone |

